hopobject.body: I work for myself naproxen bodybuilding Kullman said DuPont expects to see modest earnings growth for the year, despite continued hardship in its performance chemicals unit, which includes titanium dioxide, or TiO2. The performance chemicals unit saw volume increase 12 percent in the third quarter, but that was not enough to offset steep price declines for titanium dioxide, refrigerants and fluoropolymers, along with higher raw material inventory costs. The unit's operating earnings fell $159 million to $254 million.
